<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Thank You for Contacting WebVirtus</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        background: #ffffff;
        margin: 40px auto;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .logo {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .logo img {
        width: 120px;
        height: auto;
      }
      h2 {
        color: #007bff;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      blockquote {
        background: #f0f4ff;
        border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
        padding: 12px 16px;
        margin: 15px 0;
        font-style: italic;
        color: #444;
      }
      a {
        color: #007bff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 25px;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #888;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .signature {
        margin-top: 25px;
        color: #444;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">
        <img
          src="https://ik.imagekit.io/aalam855/webvirtus/webVirtusLogo.png?updatedAt=1760770122877"
          alt="WebVirtus Logo"
        />
      </div>

      <h2>Thank You for Reaching Out, <%= name %>!</h2>

      <p>
        We truly appreciate you contacting <strong>WebVirtus</strong>. Your
        message has been successfully received and forwarded to our support
        team.
      </p>

      <p><strong>Here’s what you sent us:</strong></p>
      <blockquote><%= message %></blockquote>

      <p>
        Our experts will carefully review your message and get back to you as
        soon as possible — typically within
        <strong>24 to 48 hours</strong>.
      </p>

      <p>
        In the meantime, feel free to explore our projects and services at
        <a href="https://webvirtus.it.com" target="_blank">webvirtus.it.com</a>.
      </p>

      <div class="signature">
        <p>Warm regards,<br /><strong>Team WebVirtus</strong></p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> WebVirtus. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
